asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

name: Roxy
description:
Roxy isn’t your Mansions and Lambos kind of Fluf. She was born and raised deep in the burrows of the Dunes. Her father was a Dune Degen who left for the Mycelium trade and her mother was always working two shifts at The Bunny Ranch. Roxy was left behind at an early age to fend for herself. She’s a rough and rugged Fluf that’s known for her No Fxcks Tonight attitude amongst what she considers her real family, The Dune Crew. 

Roxy’s tough knuckled reputation spread throughout Fluf World. Many of those outside of the Dune Crew only knew her as, The Bouncer. This sharp tongued Fluf could party like a Rockstar but you’d better think twice before saying anything bad about the Dunes or her beloved humies in Dune Crew.

description: PSILOSOFUR is the psilocybin-fueled philosopher, born with the ability to detect truth and travel in and out of metaverse portals at will. A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

name: H.R. Fluf N Stuff
description:
In the 70’s Sid and Marty Krofft felt that a new TV series was needed to fill a broadcast spot for Children.
H.R. Fluf N Stuff was born. They were sure that this was going to be a winner. But no sooner had they announced the project in the industry mags than Bugs Bunny over at Warner’s took a Cease and Desist out against them. Bugs wanted to be the only star bunny on the TV at the time.  (Besides those pesky Playboy Bunnies down at the Mansion!) So, Sid and Marty were left with no choice but to reinvent their show and the wonderful and instant classic that is H.R. PufnStuf was born. 
The Bunny that was going to play the lead for H.R. Fluf N Stuff can be found these days at the main street bar down in Reno three nights a week. As he is showing his years - he’s having to dye his fur orange and has a collection of comedy pirate hats that have become an important part of his schtick. Tip him if you see him.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)
